---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Cigna Global in Indonesia', level: 2 },
  { id: 'indonesia-network', text: 'Network Coverage', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'evacuation', text: 'Medical Evacuation', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose Cigna', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Indonesia', href: '/countries/indonesia/insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'Cigna vs Allianz', href: '/compare/cigna-global-vs-allianz-care' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'indoPrice', header: 'Indonesia (Age 35)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Silver', coverage: 'Inpatient + Day-patient', indoPrice: '$120-160/mo' },
  { plan: 'Gold', coverage: 'Silver + Outpatient', indoPrice: '$160-220/mo' },
  { plan: 'Platinum', coverage: 'Gold + Enhanced', indoPrice: '$220-300/mo' },
];

const hospitalColumns = [
  { key: 'location', header: 'Location' },
  { key: 'hospitals', header: 'Network Hospitals' },
  { key: 'directBilling', header: 'Direct Billing' },
];

const hospitalRows = [
  { location: 'Bali', hospitals: 'BIMC Hospital (Kuta & Nusa Dua), Siloam Hospitals, Kasih Ibu', directBilling: true },
  { location: 'Jakarta', hospitals: 'Pondok Indah Hospital, RS Medistra, Siloam Hospitals', directBilling: true },
  { location: 'Surabaya', hospitals: 'National Hospital, Siloam Hospitals Surabaya', directBilling: true },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Cigna Global Health Insurance in Indonesia"
  description="Complete guide to using Cigna Global in Indonesia and Bali. Local network, evacuation coverage, pricing, and comparison to other options."
  headline="Cigna Global Health Insurance in Indonesia"
  subheadline="Comprehensive international coverage for expats in Indonesia and Bali."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/indonesia-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a Cigna Indonesia Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Cigna Global in Indonesia</h2>
  <p>
    Cigna Global is a top choice for serious expats in Indonesia who want comprehensive coverage. With high limits ($1-3M), strong evacuation benefits, and direct billing at major Indonesian hospitals, Cigna provides the security that's essential in a country where medical evacuation may be necessary.
  </p>
  <p>
    For digital nomads, Cigna may be overkill. But for long-term expats, families, or anyone with health concerns, it's worth the premium.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$1-3M</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Annual coverage limits</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Included</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Medical evacuation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">24/7</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Emergency support</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get an Indonesia-Specific Quote"
    description="See what Cigna Global costs for expats in Indonesia."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="indonesia-network">Network Coverage in Indonesia</h2>
  <p>
    Cigna has direct billing arrangements at Indonesia's top private hospitals:
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={hospitalColumns} rows={hospitalRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Bali Coverage</h3>
  <p>
    BIMC Hospital (locations in Kuta and Nusa Dua) is the premier international-standard hospital in Bali. Cigna has direct billing here, making cashless treatment straightforward.
  </p>

  <h3>Jakarta Coverage</h3>
  <p>
    Jakarta has more hospital options with world-class facilities like Pondok Indah Hospital. If you need specialized care beyond Bali's capabilities, Jakarta is typically the first destination.
  </p>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Which Plan for Indonesia?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Silver:</strong> Inpatient only. Pay routine care out of pocket (affordable in Indonesia).</li>
    <li><strong>Gold:</strong> Practical choice with outpatient coverage included.</li>
    <li><strong>Platinum:</strong> Maximum coverage with enhanced mental health and wellness.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="evacuation">Medical Evacuation</h2>
  <p>
    Medical evacuation coverage is crucial in Indonesia. Cigna Global includes evacuation benefits that cover transport to Singapore, Australia, or your home country if local facilities can't provide needed care.
  </p>
  <p>
    This is especially important if you're based in Bali or other islands outside Java—evacuation costs can exceed $50,000-100,000.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose Cigna in Indonesia</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Long-term expats and families</li>
        <li>Those with health concerns</li>
        <li>Retirees on KITAS</li>
        <li>Anyone wanting comprehensive coverage</li>
        <li>Those prioritizing evacuation benefits</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Consider Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Short-term digital nomads (SafetyWing)</li>
        <li>Budget-conscious healthy expats (IMG)</li>
        <li>Those on tourist visas only</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready for Coverage in Indonesia?"
    description="Get a personalized Cigna Global quote."
    buttonText="Get Your Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Verify coverage details directly with Cigna before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
